Richard Gere is more cynical.
The two films “The Hunting Party” and “Moerderischer Frieden” are again devoted to the war in the Balkans.
Both were not very convinced.
Either the concepts are fixed too much on action and shooting, or the two films are too exciting.
Richard Gere with his "The Hunting Party" can not help in this case either.
At the beginning there was good news: Karadzic and Mladic, the war criminals, continue to hide in the mountains of the Balkans, but precisely there, in the dark interior of the country during the Bosnian war, actor Richard Gere was discovered again.
